  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="8461032">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/8461032/" class="title-link">人歌小岁酒，花舞大唐春</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-8461032"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/63372761/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u63372761-5.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/63372761/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">月华流照君</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2017-04-05"
      class="main-meta">2017-04-05 23:05:54</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_8461032_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  陆陆续续花了大概一周时间草草读完了，用日记的形式写了一篇读书笔记。即使只是记录、整理了感兴趣的部分，也竟然有了万余字，深刻感受到自己以前参观博物馆实在是走马观花，能了解领悟到的知识实在太少太少。 唐代的文物实在是精美绝伦，可以说是叹为观止，这本书也极为耐心、...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_8461032_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_8461032_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="7868276">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7868276/" class="title-link">碰撞的繁华</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7868276"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/4486496/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u4486496-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/4486496/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">何盛华</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2016-04-26"
      class="main-meta">2016-04-26 11:07:05</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7868276_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  何家村窖藏金银器是陕西历史博物馆的镇馆之宝，也是展示大唐繁华的最重要的文物，“花舞大唐春”这句唐诗，尽显其意。这本制作精良的图册买在1年前，亲眼目睹实物之后，才拿出来仔细欣赏阅读，越发感慨。按照历史学者的研究，这几百件金银器埋藏于唐德宗年间的泾原兵变之时，为...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_7868276_full" class="hidden">
